text: Joaquín Sabriá Pitarch (born 22 August 1961) is a Spanish rowing coxswain. He competed in the men's coxed pair event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Spain Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Barcelona Category:Coxswains (rowing)
